      "title": "Atmospheric general circulation and climate",
      "abstract": "This chapter describes the energy balance of the atmosphere, the general circulation of the atmosphere and the mechanisms whereby the atmosphere transports heat and moisture. It also discusses the angular momentum balance of the atmosphere and the role it plays in determining the climate. Seasonal variations and monsoons are discussed."
